## 1. Student Registration & Setup Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User Accesses /signup] --> B{Selects Student Role}
    B --> C[Clerk Authentication<br/>Google/Email]
    C --> D[Redirect to /dashboard]
    D --> E[GET /api/auth/set-role]
    E --> F{needsSetup?}
    F -->|true| G[Redirect to /setup/unified]
    F -->|false| H[Access Student Portal]

    G --> I[3-Step Setup Wizard]
    I --> J[Step 1: Personal Info]
    J --> K[Step 2: Class Selection]
    K --> L[Step 3: Learning Preferences]

    L --> M[POST /api/setup/student]
    M --> N{User exists in DB?}
    N -->|No| O[Create users record]
    N -->|Yes| P[Update users record]

    O --> Q[Create students record]
    P --> Q
    Q --> R[Set onboardingComplete: true]
    R --> S[Redirect to /student/dashboard]

    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style C fill:#fef3c7
    style O fill:#d4edda
    style Q fill:#d4edda
    style S fill:#c3e6cb
```

**API Endpoint:** `POST /api/setup/student`

**Database Tables:**
1. `users` - Create or update user record
2. `students` - Create student-specific record
3. `classes` - Link student to class
4. `schools` - Link student to school

**Request Body:**
```typescript
{
  firstName: string,
  lastName: string,
  email: string,
  phone: string,
  dateOfBirth: string,
  grade: number,
  section: string,
  interests: string[],
  goals: string[]
}
```

