## 2. School Admin Application & Approval Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User Signs Up as School Admin] --> B[POST /api/setup/school-admin]
    B --> C[Create users record]
    C --> D[Create school_admin_applications<br/>status: pending_approval]
    D --> E[Redirect to /pending-approval]

    E --> F{Platform Admin Action}
    F --> G[GET /api/admin/school-admin-applications]
    G --> H[View All Applications]

    H --> I{Review Decision}
    I -->|Approve| J[POST /api/admin/school-admin-applications/:id/approve]
    I -->|Reject| K[POST /api/admin/school-admin-applications/:id/reject]

    J --> L[Verify Payment]
    L --> M[Update application status: approved]
    M --> N[Update users.type: school-admin]
    N --> O[INSERT into user_roles<br/>role: school-admin]
    O --> P[Link users.schoolId]
    P --> Q[Send Approval Email]

    Q --> R[User Can Access<br/>/school-admin]

    K --> S[Update application status: rejected]
    S --> T[Send Rejection Email]

    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style D fill:#fff3cd
    style J fill:#d4edda
    style M fill:#d4edda
    style N fill:#d4edda
    style O fill:#d4edda
    style S fill:#f8d7da
```

**API Endpoints:**
- `POST /api/setup/school-admin` - Submit application
- `GET /api/admin/school-admin-applications` - List applications
- `POST /api/admin/school-admin-applications/:id/approve` - Approve
- `POST /api/admin/school-admin-applications/:id/reject` - Reject

**Database Tables:**
1. `users` - User record
2. `school_admin_applications` - Application tracking
3. `user_roles` - Role assignment
4. `schools` - School linkage

