## 3. Career Matching Flow (Assessment → AI → Career)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Student Takes Assessment] --> B[POST /api/student/assessments]
    B --> C[Store assessment_results<br/>RIASEC/MBTI/DISC]

    C --> D[AI Career Matching Engine]
    D --> E[Fetch Student Data]
    E --> F[Get assessment scores]
    E --> G[Get academic performance]
    E --> H[Get interests & goals]

    F --> I[Compare with Career Database]
    G --> I
    H --> I

    I --> J[Calculate Match Scores]
    J --> K[Sort by relevance]
    K --> L[Return Top 10 Careers]

    L --> M[Store in career_matches]
    M --> N[Display on /student/careers]

    N --> O{Student Interacts}
    O -->|Save Career| P[POST /api/saved-careers]
    O -->|Ask AI| Q[POST /api/ai/career]

    Q --> R[AI Career Coach]
    R --> S[Context: Bhutan-specific]
    R --> T[RUB Colleges Data]
    R --> U[BCSE Requirements]
    R --> V[Career Guidance]

    style A fill:#ff9966
    style C fill:#ffd9b3
    style J fill:#d4edda
    style L fill:#d4edda
    style R fill:#e8f5e9
    style V fill:#c3e6cb
```

**API Endpoints:**
- `POST /api/student/assessments` - Submit assessment
- `GET /api/student/careers` - Get career matches
- `POST /api/ai/career` - AI career advice
- `POST /api/saved-careers` - Save career

**Database Tables:**
1. `assessments` - Assessment definitions
2. `assessment_results` - Student scores
3. `riasec_results` - RIASEC specific
4. `mbti_results` - MBTI specific
5. `disc_results` - DISC specific
6. `career_matches` - Match results
7. `careers` - Career catalog
8. `rub_colleges` - College data
9. `ai_interactions` - AI chat logs

