## 5. Invoice & Billing Cycle Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Monthly Billing Cycle] --> B[POST /api/admin/billing/generate-invoices]
    B --> C[For each active school]
    C --> D[Get subscription tier]
    D --> E[Calculate amount<br/>Based on tier & usage]

    E --> F[CREATE invoice record<br/>status: draft]
    F --> G[Send invoice email]
    G --> H[Update invoice.status: pending]

    H --> I{School Payment}
    I -->|Pay Online| J[POST /api/billing/invoices/:id/pay]
    I -->|Bank Transfer| K[Admin verifies]

    J --> L[Payment Gateway]
    L --> M[Update payment records]
    M --> N[Update invoice.status: paid]

    K --> O[POST /api/admin/schools/:id/invoices/:id/record-payment]
    O --> N

    N --> P[GET /api/admin/stats<br/>Revenue updated]

    style A fill:#ec4899
    style F fill:#ffd9b3
    style L fill:#d4edda
    style N fill:#c3e6cb
    style P fill:#e8f5e9
```

**API Endpoints:**
- `POST /api/admin/billing/generate-invoices` - Generate invoices
- `GET /api/billing/invoices` - List invoices
- `GET /api/billing/invoices/:id` - Get invoice
- `POST /api/billing/invoices/:id/pay` - Pay invoice
- `POST /api/admin/schools/:id/invoices/:id/record-payment` - Record payment
- `GET /api/admin/stats` - Revenue stats

**Database Tables:**
1. `invoices` - Invoice records
2. `payment_transactions` - Payment records
3. `subscriptions` - Active subscriptions
4. `schools` - School billing info
5. `subscription_plans` - Plan pricing

