## Data Flow Architecture

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph "Frontend"
        UI[React Components]
    end

    subgraph "API Layer"
        ROUTE[API Routes<br/>src/app/api/*/route.ts]
    end

    subgraph "Business Logic"
        AUTH[requireAuth<br/>Permission checks]
        LOGIC[Business Logic<br/>Validation, processing]
    end

    subgraph "Data Layer"
        ORM[Drizzle ORM]
        DB[(PostgreSQL)]
    end

    subgraph "External Services"
        CLERK[Clerk Auth]
        AI[AI/LLM Service]
        PAYMENT[Payment Gateway]
    end

    UI --> ROUTE
    ROUTE --> AUTH
    AUTH --> LOGIC
    LOGIC --> ORM
    ORM --> DB

    AUTH --> CLERK
    LOGIC --> AI
    LOGIC --> PAYMENT

    style UI fill:#e1f5ff
    style ROUTE fill:#fef3c7
    style AUTH fill:#ffd9b3
    style LOGIC fill:#d4edda
    style ORM fill:#c3e6cb
    style DB fill:#a7f3d0
```

